class Solution:
     def findTheDifference(self, s, t):
         """
         :type s: str
         :type t: str
         :rtype: str
         """
         ss = sorted(s)
         st = sorted(t)
         i = 0 
         j = 0
         while i <= len(ss) - 1:
             if ss[i] == st[j]:
                 i += 1
                 j += 1
             else: return st[j]
         return st[j]

class Solution:
     def findTheDifference(self, s, t):
         """
         :type s: str
         :type t: str
         :rtype: str
         """
         return [i for i in t if i not in s or s.count(i)!=t.count(i)][0]

class Solution:
     def findTheDifference(self, s, t):
         """
         :type s: str
         :type t: str
         :rtype: str
         """
         a = list(s)
         b = list(t)
         for c in s:
             a.remove(c)
             b.remove(c)
         return b[0]

class Solution:
     def findTheDifference(self, s, t):
         """
         :type s: str
         :type t: str
         :rtype: str
         """
         S = [i for i in s]
         T = [i for i in t]
         for i in S:
             T.remove(i)
         return T[0]
